overview: Young Lily is going door to door offering training services when she encounters two very wild animals.  Jynx falls right into a couple's perverted trap. Lucky for her, they give her a real easy way out.  Melanie could really use the help of a tutor but to her surprise she became the hands on subject.  Ella is locked out of her house when a couple spots her. Back at their house she discovers they wanted more than to just wait with her.  Victoria and her boyfriend are caught hanging at the neighbor's pool. Are the neighbors angry or have they found a clever way to get rid of her man?
title: Couples Seeking Teens 5
